Eel Mines
Underground Settlement
Undeground Town
Eel Fortress
Various valuable resources are mined by sea creatures in these mines
These mines have grown into a small underground settlement where sea creatures live and work
This underground settlement grew into a small town. Many of the sea creatures living here have not seen the sun for years and are quite content with it

This underground town has grown into a full-fledged underground fortress, extremely difficult to siege. Nonetheless, legends are popular among Sea Creaturess about ruined and abandoned underground fortresses destroyed by three turtles, a disgruntled Manatee, a party, and a lots of vulcanic magma
